        "subject": "LU-3399 ldlm: report last_committed value using export/obd",
        "message": "LU-3399 ldlm: report last_committed value using export/obd\n\nBoth export and obd value is used for report last_committed value.\nPatch takes into account obd_last_transno number when reporting last\ncommit transaction number to the client. This helps for client with\nopen/close activity to get real commit number and free requests from\nreplay queue.\n\nSigned-off-by: Alexander Boyko <alexander_boyko@xyratex.com>\nSigned-off-by: Alexey Lyashkov <alexey_lyashkov@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: Ibf58124758a5ba12f36212a41b71260e03bcc166\n"
